Not only are there to be no races this year, but it is announced that the famous old track is to be abandoned and that the ground upon which it is located will be cut up into city lots and sold.

abstract: The report of the Buffalo. Rochester and Pittsburg Railway Company for the year ended June 30 last shows gross earnings of $8,161,079, an increase of $631.121.
